Story: Regex Pattern Matching and Extraction Tests

Given:
  email: String = "user@example.com"
  phone: String = "Call me at 555-123-4567 or 555-987-6543"
  text: String = "hello123world"
  is_valid: Integer = 0
  has_digit: Integer = 0
  first_phone: String = ""

Step 1
  Because: Test simple MATCHES pattern
  Then: is_valid becomes email MATCHES "user"
  Then: PRINT is_valid

Step 2
  Because: Test digit pattern
  Then: has_digit becomes text MATCHES "\\d"
  Then: PRINT has_digit

Step 3
  Because: Extract simple pattern
  Then: first_phone becomes EXTRACT "\\d{3}" FROM phone
  Then: PRINT first_phone

End: Return first_phone
  Because: Basic regex tests completed
